<br>
You'll find that words of bondage and wings of rathe and breath of ro etc for your higher level spell research will be found in Seb and planes.<br>
<br>
Try to join some of these raids with the new raid feature you'll see what people are looting and you can ask them for it.<br>
<br>
I used to keep a stockpile of lvl 49 pet research components but destroyed them all long ago for bank space.  <br>
<br>
Try heading to Sebilis and at the zone in send some tells to the clerics or enchanters and ask them to keep an eye open for the components you're looking for.  <br>
<br>
They will likely be kind enough to send you a tell if they loot a research component.<br>
