<br>
In the last 2 weeks I found a drop of pure rain, 2 foul smelling liquids, 9 or 10 clockwork gears and bolts, 2 clockwork carapaces, midnight stone, etc<br>
<br>
I bought them all for dirt cheap - nothing cost more than 24 to 25 pp or so.  I sold them for:<br>
<br>
Drop of pure rain: 5k  (yes 5k!)<br>
2 x foul smelling liquids: 2k each<br>
9 x clock work gears / bolts: 100 pp each<br>
carapaces: 100 pp each<br>
Midnight stone: 750 pp<br>
<br>
These prices were from people auctioning that they were buying these components for those prices - way way higher than I would have thought to sell them for.<br>
<br>
I find this stuff abandoned on npc merchants constantly - its like free pp!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Look up ingredients for the high level tradeskills, then see what they sell for in the bazaar - then make a list to watch for and check merchants as you go by (especially PoK / PoT merchants)<br>
<br>
Limpy<br>
<br>
