If you go trough bazaar NPC merchants, Thurgadin merchants, and maybe overthere(if not kos) you can find a lot of interesting items(including words and other research items), another used to be good spot is merchants in fungus grove, found a lot of essence of sunlight there that a bard payed 100pp for(payed a few plats), found a club of the ice ocean to for 125pp, sold in bazaar for 1500 in like 5 minutes <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , seems the place is a bit deserted now after PoP.<br>
